{
  "stem": "1641.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 3.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "I won't-- I won't touch it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So conditions were very bad.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Then we got our tattoos next morning.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Everybody had burnt in their number.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We started with capital A 12,000 like-- oh, my number was 12139.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we found that capital A was necessary because previously 200,000 people had their tattoos, and as they got to the number of 200,000, then the Germans said let's start again with 0.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then they put a A-series.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The A-series went from 0 up to 20,000, and then by July the B-- the B-series started.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "We met the B people later on.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "B always meant that they only arrived in July '44, July-August.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The A-series, they-- they all arrived in 1944.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Anybody who had a number between 100,000 and 200,000 was 1943, and anybody with a very small number must have been there since 1941-- with a number of, say, 27,000.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Oh, that was very, very, very few people.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Each time you met somebody with a number under 100,000, you-- you really had the highest regard for him, because he survived there three or four years.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "So he had-- must have had a good position or some extremely heavy physique.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Anyhow, they got our numbers.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "The sleeping conditions were shocking.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "It was four people in each bunk, four-level bunk.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "It was-- just to climb up to the top was hard enough, and then four legs came into your mouth and the other four legs went into the other people's face, of course.",
      "word_count": 33
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "And kicking, shouting.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It's people kicking each other all night.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And each time there was a noise, the commander came there with his stick and kept shut up, you bastards!",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "All of you make so much noise.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
